    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of this car\u2014it\u2019s basically in showroom condition. I\u2019m talking a totally spotless interior, flawless paint, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one, and it\u2019s finally time for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It\u2019s a total gem and ready for your next big adventure! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look and get behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
