    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition; the premium leather still carries its original factory aroma and remains perfectly taut with no bolster wear. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive binder of service records documenting every preventative measure taken since new. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
