    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This beauty is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is basically flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
