    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for precise torque vectoring. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to address chassis fatigue common to the platform. The suspension retains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution, enhanced by refreshed bushings and dampers. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition with consistent paint depth and factory-tight panel gaps, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and meticulous preventative maintenance.",
